item.title: Exploring the Relationship Between Vitamin D Levels and Hospital Readmissions
item.description: Exploring the Relationship Between Vitamin D Levels and Hospital Readmissions Description This project investigated whether a relationship exists between a patient’s Vitamin D levels and their likelihood of being readmitted to the hospital within 30 days of discharge.
